{"tid":2274160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門山景邨麥當勞打人案　體內含可卡因的施襲男子最終被判社服令","createTime":"2020-11-06T08:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T05:29:21.000Z","uid":22556,"like":19,"dislike":263,"uniUserReply":114,"replies":[{"pid":"916f8f29d24c55a8dbb026c36cca93d6235325ca","tid":2274160,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:55:39.000Z","msg":"屯門山景邨麥當勞快餐店經理要求顧客戴口罩而被打傷，其中一名男子早前承認襲擊致造成身體傷害等罪，被判160小時社會服務令。 <br />\n<br />\n案發在7月14日凌晨，報稱任職貨車司機的被告張易揚，在屯門山景邨麥當勞快餐店點餐時沒戴口罩，餐廳經理上前勸諭，被告拒絕並打傷對方；又損壞收銀機顯示屏。<br />\n<br />\n被告早前承認襲擊致造成身體傷害及刑事毁壞兩罪，驗尿報告早前顯示，被告體內含可卡因；辯方求情指，最新驗尿報告結果為陰性，被告已悔改，願意做社會服務，希望法庭給予機會。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官最終判處160小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n屯門山景邨麥當勞打人案　施襲男子被判社服令<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=411896&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411896%26refer%3DShare&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9mAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=b08a43a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411896%26refer%3DShare&h=b460c085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=411896&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"ee9cec55e209b109fb3a90226af3d77b6e8cdc82","tid":2274160,"uid":810,"like":114,"dislike":1,"score":113,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:56:20.000Z","msg":"喂 自己人自己人"},{"pid":"4dc4a6dde202a6dac2fb89302ea900ab095e5ba0","tid":2274160,"uid":71728,"like":125,"dislike":0,"score":125,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:56:59.000Z","msg":"幫D狗開先例 第日吸毒開槍亂殺人都可以判社會服務令"},{"pid":"89992cb07ddd8e16e47b32c43005e43711760a65","tid":2274160,"uid":39215,"like":294,"dislike":3,"score":291,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:57:26.000Z","msg":"扔個鐵罐出馬路就坐55日<br />\n打人 藏毒就唔駛坐<br />\nover my dead body!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class